com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange

Class DataExchangeExportXMLSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.DataExchangeSpec
      • com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.DataExchangeExportSpec
        • com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.DataExchangeExportXMLSpec
  • Deprecated. 
    Since 2.3.0, replaced by DataExchangeSpec.

    public final class DataExchangeExportXMLSpec
extends DataExchangeExportSpec
    Stores specifications for EBX® Data Exchange Add-on Export XML service. Specifications have extra options include exporting computed values, indented XML and omitting XML comment.
    Since:
    2.1.0
    See Also:
